snippet: The police in New Delhi arrested a third man on Thursday in connection with the gang-rape of a Danish tourist and said they were still seeking five other men.
abstract: Police in New Delhi arrest Bhagat Singh in connection with gang rape of 51-year-old Danish tourist; Singh is third man arrested in case; police are still searching for five other suspects.
lead_paragraph: The police in New Delhi arrested a third man on Thursday in connection with the gang-rape of a Danish tourist and said they were still seeking five other men.

headline.main: India: 3rd Arrest in Rape of Danish Tourist
headline.print_headline: India: 3rd Arrest in Rape of Tourist
